Title: JRuby and Sorbet
Description: A recent tweet by the JRuby folks, let me know that the work I had done a while ago to get Sorbet working seemed to have gone under the radar. Sorbet is a fast, powerful type checker designed for Ruby. I wanted to reflect on it’s use at our current codebase, challenges still faced and where to go next. If you want to cut ahead and start using Sorbet right away, I’ve contributed some documentation.
